<plot>Documentary for WE / Women's Entertainment Channel on the sensual appeal of vampires. Interviewees include authors Nancy Collins and Anne Rice, filmmakers David Goyer and John Landis, actress Ann Manguson ("The Hunger"), New York Times film critic Elvis Mitchell, "Buffy the Vampire Slayer" writer-producer Marti Noxon, and horror-film / erotic-film author-lecturer Maitland McDonagh.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?395781</url></doc>
